quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  28,29,FELEMMA KADA MUSAL-’EXHELE WE SARE BI’EHLIHI ‘ANESE MIN XHANIBIT-TURI NARÆN KALE LI’HLIHI EMKUTHU ‘INNI ‘ANESTU NARÆN LE’ALLI ‘ATIKUM MINHA BIHABERIN ‘EW XHEDHWETIN MINE EN-NARI LE’ALLEKUM TESTELUNE
  28,30,FELEMMA ‘ETAHA NUDI MIN SHATI’IL-WADIL-’EJMENI FIL-BUK’ATIL-MUBAREKETI MINE ESH-SHEXHERETI ‘EN JA MUSA ‘INNI ‘ENALLAHU REBBUL-’ALEMINE
  28,31,WE ‘EN ‘ELKI ‘ASAKE FELEMMA RE’AHA TEHTEZZU KE’ENNEHA XHANNUN WELLA MUDBIRÆN WE LEM JU’AKKIB JA MUSA ‘EKBIL WE LA TEHAF ‘INNEKE MINEL-’AMININE
  28,32,ESLUK JEDEKE FI XHEJBIKE TEHRUXH BEJDA’E MIN GAJRI SU’IN WE EDMUM ‘ILEJKE XHENAHEKE MINE ER-REHBI FEDHANIKE BURHANANI MIN RABBIKE ‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHI ‘INNEHUM KANU KAWMÆN FASIKINE
  28,33,KALE RABBI ‘INNI KATELTU MINHUM NEFSÆN FE’EHAFU ‘EN JEKTULUNI
  28,34,WE ‘EHI HARUNU HUWE ‘EFSEHU MINNI LISANÆN FE’ERSILHU MA’IJE RID’ÆN JUSEDDIKUNI ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘EN JUKEDHDHIBUNI
  28,35,KALE SENESHUDDU ‘ADUDEKE BI’EHIKE WE NEXH’ALU LEKUMA SULTANÆN FELA JESILUNE ‘ILEJKUMA BI’AJATINA ‘ENTUMA WE MENI ETTEBE’AKUMAL-GALIBUNE
  28,36,FELEMMA XHA’EHUM MUSA BI’AJATINA BEJJINATIN KALU MA HADHA ‘ILLA SIHRUN MUFTEREN WE MA SEMI’NA BIHEDHA FI ‘ABA’INAL-’EWWELINE
  28,37,WE KALE MUSA RABBI ‘A’LEMU BIMEN XHA’E BIL-HUDA MIN ‘INDIHI WE MEN TEKUNU LEHU ‘AKIBETU ED-DARI ‘INNEHU LA JUFLIHU EDH-DHALIMUNE
  28,38,WE KALE FIR’AWNU JA ‘EJJUHAL-MELE’U MA ‘ALIMTU LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRI FE’EWKID LI JA HAMANU ‘ALAT-TINI FAXH’AL LI SERHÆN LE’ALLI ‘ETTELI’U ‘ILA ‘ILEHI MUSA WE ‘INNI LE’EDHUNNUHU MINEL-KADHIBINE
  28,39,WE ESTEKBERE HUWE WE XHUNUDUHU FIL-’ERDI BIGAJRIL-HEKKI WE DHENNU ‘ENNEHUM ‘ILEJNA LA JURXHA’UNE
  28,40,FE’EHADHNAHU WE XHUNUDEHU FENEBEDHNAHUM FIL-JEMMI FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETU EDH-DHALIMINE
  28,41,WE XHE’ALNAHUM ‘E’IMMETEN JED’UNE ‘ILA EN-NARI WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI LA JUNSERUNE
  28,42,WE ‘ETBA’NAHUM FI HEDHIHI ED-DUNJA LA’NETEN WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI HUM MINEL-MEKBUHINE
  28,43,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA MUSAL-KITABE MIN BA’DI MA ‘EHLEKNAL-KURUNEL-’ULA BESA’IRE LILNNASI WE HUDEN WE REHMETEN LE’ALLEHUM JETEDHEKKERUNE
  28,44,WE MA KUNTE BIXHANIBIL-GARBIJI ‘IDH KADEJNA ‘ILA MUSAL-’EMRE WE MA KUNTE MINE ESH-SHAHIDIN
  28,45,WE LEKINNA ‘ENSHE’NA KURUNÆN FETETAWELE ‘ALEJHIMUL-’UMURU WE MA KUNTE THAWIÆN FI ‘EHLI MEDJENE TETLU ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATINA WE LEKINNA KUNNA MURSILINE
  28,46,WE MA KUNTE BIXHANIBIT-TURI ‘IDH NADEJNA WE LEKIN REHMETEN MIN RABBIKE LITUNDHIRE KAWMÆN MA ‘ETAHUM MIN NEDHIRIN MIN KABLIKE LE’ALLEHUM JETEDHEKKERUNE
  28,47,WE LEWLA ‘EN TUSIBEHUM MUSIBETUN BIMA KADDEMET ‘EJDIHIM FEJEKULU REBBENA LEWLA ‘ERSELTE ‘ILEJNA RESULÆN FENETTEBI’A ‘AJATIKE WE NEKUNE MINEL-MU’UMININE
  28,48,FELEMMA XHA’EHUMUL-HEKKU MIN ‘INDINA KALU LEWLA ‘UTIJE MITHLE MA ‘UTIJE MUSA ‘EWELEM JEKFURU BIMA ‘UTIJE MUSA MIN KABLU KALU SIHRANI TEDHAHERA WE KALU ‘INNA BIKULLIN KAFIRUNE
  28,49,KUL FE’TU BIKITABIN MIN ‘INDI ELLAHI HUWE ‘EHDA MINHUMA ‘ETTEBI’HU ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  28,50,FE’IN LEM JESTEXHIBU LEKE FA’LEM ‘ENNEMA JETTEBI’UNE ‘EHWA’EHUM WE MEN ‘EDELLU MIMMENI ETTEBE’A HEWAHU BIGAJRI HUDEN MINEL-LAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JEHDIL-KAWME EDH-DHALIMINE